GamePanelX is the original free and open source game control panel.  It has been actively maintained since 2007.  

------------------------------------------------------------------------
INSTALLING
------------------------------------------------------------------------
- Download the complete Master tarball (see the Products page: http://www.gamepanelx.com/products.html)
- Extract the tarball locally
- Upload all files to your Linux hosting server
- Create a new database for gamepanelx
- Go go http://[yoursite]/gpx/install/
- Fill out everything
- Delete the "install" directory from your server
- Login 


------------------------------------------------------------------------
UPDATING
------------------------------------------------------------------------

- Download the complete Master tarball (see the Products page: http://www.gamepanelx.com/products.html)
- Extract the tarball locally
- REMOVE the "include/db.php" file
- Upload all files over your old installation
- (optional but recommended): Delete all files inside "templates_c" and "admin/templates_c"
- Run the "install/update.php" script
- Delete the "install" directory from your server
